OOC: I posted three freaking times without a single response.  He warned what 
would happen.

::Chaostaur::
       He shakes his head.  "I asked nicely for a target.  Now you are my 
target."  He puts his guns down and reassembles them into the heavy blasters 
again.  "That gets easier every time."  He fires two heavy blasts out of each 
gun at Nemesis Enforcer.
